  <Summary>Stand at attention for General Conan! The Cimmerian and his Aquilonian allies strike for the crown!

*Contents*
"When Madness Wears the Crown" - begins the adaptation of Lin Carter and L. Sprague de Camp's novel "Conan the Liberator". Adapted by Roy Thomas, John Buscema and Tony DeZuniga
~"At last it can be told! Conan leads a revolt against King Numedides of Aquilonia and his evil magician, Thulandra Thuu! A tale of wonders and wizardry on an epic scale!"~
"Chains and Fetters: A Study of Slavery in the Hyborian Age" - conclusion of the article by Jim Neal
"The Woman From Khitai" - a tale of the Hyborian Age by Don Glut, Gary Brodsky and Tony DeZuniga
A frontispiece pin-up by Tony DeZuniga</Summary>
